WEBVTT

00:00.707 --> 00:02.926
She contracted polio at six,...

00:03.339 --> 00:06.179
...survived a horrific traffic accident at 18,...

00:06.831 --> 00:10.775
...and became an iconic, internationally celebrated painter.

00:17.717 --> 00:22.783
She was underpaid, typecast, even suspended for refusing a role,...

00:23.271 --> 00:26.400
...yet became one of the biggest Hollywood stars...

00:26.560 --> 00:28.759
...and a timeless cultural icon.

00:34.757 --> 00:37.250
An outsider who dared to make her own way.

00:38.277 --> 00:41.929
She became an activist for peace and gender equality.

